    • toLoad

      public static Enemy toLoad(SaveState.EnemyData data, String textureName, int bullet_speed)
      Creates an Enemy object from saved data.
      Parameters:
      data - The saved enemy data.
      textureName - The name of the texture used for the enemy.
      bullet_speed - The speed of the bullets fired by the enemy.
      Returns:
      An Enemy object initialized with the data.
